ActQuarantine Act
SubjectOrder Repealing the Minimizing the Risk of Exposure to COVID-19 in Canada Order
PrecisORDER REPEALING THE MINIMIZING THE RISK OF EXPOSURE TO COVID-19 IN CANADA ORDER in order to repeal the requirements for persons entering Canada on a flight itinerary originating from the People’s Republic of China (China), Hong Kong Special Administrative Region of the People’s Republic of China (Hong Kong) or Macao Special Administrative Region of the People’s Republic of China (Macao).
